headline.main: Mrs. Agnew's Knitting Is Another Victim Of Her Husband's Mediterranean Victory

lead_paragraph: GOSPORT, England, Nov. 9 -- A woman sat in the parlor of her home here tonight knitting a jumper. At 9 P.M. she turned on the radio for the news and heard that the British had wiped out an Italian convoy in the Mediterranean.
abstract: Mrs Agnew hears broadcast of victory, Gosport, Eng
